those temporary holding cells

20:09.208 --> 20:10.626
they started on the first day.

20:15.548 --> 20:17.341
<i>They say, like, relapse is real easy,</i>

20:17.883 --> 20:20.302
<i>like a devil's way of saying,
you know, I want you back.</i>

20:22.346 --> 20:25.266
<i>But the sponsor in the NA meetings
in jail,</i>

20:25.349 --> 20:27.727
<i>she said, I will support you
through it all when you get out.</i>

20:31.147 --> 20:34.817
My grandma, she's been back in Germany,
I think maybe 10 years.

20:34.900 --> 20:38.404
<i>But she comes back every year
or every other year.</i>

20:39.029 --> 20:43.033
<i>And right when she gets here I get locked
up so I don't never get to see her.</i>

20:44.535 --> 20:45.870
<i>She raised me.</i>

20:46.287 --> 20:49.915
<i>And she's like one of the main reasons
why I wanna go straight.</i>

20:49.999 --> 20:51.792
<i>She's... my backbone.</i>

20:54.378 --> 20:55.379
I can't wait.

20:56.046 --> 20:57.840
I just want to smell the fresh air.

20:59.091 --> 21:01.010
I can imagine it's beautiful outside.

21:09.351 --> 21:10.478
My old lady, bro.

21:11.020 --> 21:14.273
She gonna chew my ass out.
I'm like, no, I really wasn't doing shit.

21:14.356 --> 21:16.484
I was trying to catch a ride
to pay my rent.

21:16.567 --> 21:19.028
And that was it.
She know my car fucked up.

21:19.111 --> 21:22.072
Shit. I'm just living life
trying to maintain, man.

21:23.282 --> 21:25.117
- Hello.
<i>- Hello?</i>

21:25.618 --> 21:27.036
