21:30.915 --> 21:33.042
and see if you can swipe me out.

21:33.125 --> 21:35.252
<i>Okay, if I cannot swipe you out...</i>

21:35.336 --> 21:36.587
Go get the money.

21:36.670 --> 21:38.172
You got me out of jail before, Shonda.

21:38.255 --> 21:40.508
Why you acting like you don't know
what the fuck you doing?

21:40.591 --> 21:42.092
<i>I'm trying to figure out if I...</i>

21:42.176 --> 21:45.471
<i>I gotta go to work... I have to go
to work this morning. Yes, I do.</i>

21:45.554 --> 21:46.514
Oh, my God.

21:47.306 --> 21:50.768
Man, I'm dead to you.
At least consider me dead to you.

21:50.893 --> 21:54.980
You actually went to work tonight, not
concerned about what the fuck is going on.

21:55.064 --> 21:56.190
And then you plan on going to work again?

21:56.273 --> 21:58.567
<i>No! Wait. Let me cut you the fuck off!</i>

21:58.651 --> 22:00.736
<i>I'm fucking doing shit
I ain't gotta fucking do!</i>

22:01.362 --> 22:03.280
The relationship I have with my girl...

22:04.031 --> 22:06.033
it ain't the best, but...

22:06.534 --> 22:10.079
I'm not faulting her for what I do
with this situation right now.

22:10.162 --> 22:12.122
I gotta depend on her because I'm in jail.

22:13.249 --> 22:16.252
My girl makes... more money than me.

22:17.002 --> 22:19.755
No, you just told me you're doing shit
that you ain't...

22:20.381 --> 22:22.716
<i>Man... listen! Stop calling me!</i>

22:22.800 --> 22:24.635
<i>I gotta fucking work
