23:25.029 --> 23:26.322
All right, everybody up!

23:26.405 --> 23:29.575
Set the phones down, set the phones down.
No, don't hang up, you'll be right back.

23:29.658 --> 23:31.660
Everybody come out,
'cause I can't find my guy.

23:32.536 --> 23:33.370
Go down.

23:35.122 --> 23:36.373
I'm looking for a person.

23:36.999 --> 23:38.334
