23:48.385 --> 23:51.680
Take your fucking charge!
Take your charge, nigga.

23:53.015 --> 23:54.099
Take your charge.

23:55.184 --> 23:57.353
You're scaring him.
That's what's going on.

23:57.895 --> 24:00.731
I'll put hands on that boy.
I'll get him fucked up!

24:00.814 --> 24:02.900
I got this. Trust me, I got this.

24:03.400 --> 24:07.196
You gotta tell that man not to do
the bullshit. He gonna do the bullshit.

24:08.155 --> 24:09.823
