go away for, for life.

24:49.196 --> 24:50.656
All right, grab your bin.

24:54.118 --> 24:55.244
Right. Yep.

24:55.869 --> 24:58.580
Go and see this gentleman up there.

24:59.498 --> 25:00.457
Thank you.

25:01.834 --> 25:04.545
Ow, I'm so excited!
Oh, my God, oh, my God!

25:06.630 --> 25:08.090
<i>I'm not going to the streets.</i>

25:08.841 --> 25:11.885
<i>I'm not going to use,
I'm going to my family.</i>

25:13.804 --> 25:17.307
<i>'Cause I can't go to the streets
and stay clean. It's not going to work.</i>

25:23.772 --> 25:26.442
- Clip that tag to the top of your shirt.
- Yes, ma'am.

25:26.525 --> 25:27.443
<i>I'm anxious.</i>

25:27.985 --> 25:30.195
<i>I guess, nervous and scared
at the same time.</i>

25:31.363 --> 25:32.197
Freedom.

25:32.656 --> 25:34.700
<i>I'm really worried
that it's not going to go well.</i>

25:42.708 --> 25:44.918
- Hey, Shantee!
- Hey!

25:46.003 --> 25:46.879
Hey!

25:47.713 --> 25:48.839
Aww...

25:52.176 --> 25:53.427
Hey, Tamaya!

25:54.136 --> 25:55.971
Aww, hey!

25:56.055 --> 25:58.390
- Good to see you. How are you?
- Fine.

25:59.391 --> 26:00.601
Pretty shoes!

26:00.684 --> 26:02.686
How you doing? You excited?

26:07.357 --> 26:10.444
- How long were you in jail?
- I was in jail 45 days.

26:11.236 --> 26:13.238
I don't think that's
long enough time there.

26:13.322 --> 26:15.783
What you mean?
How long do you want me to do, a year?

26:15.908 --> 26:17.242
Or two, or three.

26:17.326 --> 26:18.410
Good night!

26:18.994 --> 26:20.370
Why would you wish that on me?

26:20.454 --> 26:23.457
I just want this to be it.
Like, can this be it?

26:23.540 --> 26:26.460
Can this time be the last time,
like, please?

26:28.587 --> 26:29.421
It is.

26:32.633 --> 26:33.675
I hope so.

26:58.200 --> 27:01.703
I love you. It's like I lost a part of you
when you got locked up.

27:04.123 --> 27:06.208
You don't know how long
I've waited for this day.

27:08.418 --> 27:09.795
Really, you don't.

27:11.130 --> 27:12.965
I'm so glad you're out.

27:23.433 --> 27:26.270
Oh, I'm so glad to be out.
I'm so glad to go home.

27:30.566 --> 27:32.860
- Ain't that where you had a heart attack?
- Yes, ma'am.

27:32.943 --> 27:35.904
- They let me go there.
- You weren't but, what, 19, 20?

27:35.988 --> 27:36.864
Yes, ma'am.

27:37.865 --> 27:40.075
- Remember you took me to the hospital?
- I remember.

28:01.430 --> 28:03.932
<i>To accept this free call,
press one.</i>

28:04.016 --> 28:05.601
