28:05.976 --> 28:06.935
Hello?

28:07.728 --> 28:08.562
<i>Yeah?</i>

28:09.521 --> 28:11.690
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

28:12.900 --> 28:15.819
Shonda, I love you,
