28:16.695 --> 28:21.366
I just need you to... I just need you
to just try to bond me out tonight.

28:21.450 --> 28:25.037
<i>Dre, I'm taking off work early
to get your ass out of jail.</i>

28:25.120 --> 28:26.997
Thank you, thank you, Shonda.

28:27.080 --> 28:29.082
Thank you, Shonda.

28:29.708 --> 28:31.001
<i>I'm fucking tired of this.</i>

28:31.084 --> 28:32.002
Thank you, Shonda.

28:32.085 --> 28:33.045
<i>I'm fucking tired of this shit.</i>

28:33.128 --> 28:34.129
Thank you, Shonda.

