As a brother, I worry 'bout how mine gonna
feel just 'cause we weren't on good terms.

28:41.887 --> 28:45.891
You know what I'm saying, like, yeah,
you my baby mama and all of that shit

28:45.974 --> 28:48.268
but, at the same time,
I need you to handle shit like this.

28:48.352 --> 28:51.104
