28:51.188 --> 28:54.274
Now I got to prove I ain't no dope nigga,
you know what I'm saying?

28:58.320 --> 28:59.446
Hey, listen up.

29:00.113 --> 29:02.991
Mr. Thomas, Andre.
Thomas, Andre.

29:05.619 --> 29:08.497
Go through that door there.
Have a seat on the bench to your left.

29:09.748 --> 29:11.166
<i>Yeah, I'mma get a good lawyer.</i>

29:11.291 --> 29:13.543
<i>I'mma fight the case,
plead not guilty,</i>

29:13.627 --> 29:16.213
<i>and I'm not thinking negative.
I'm going to beat it.</i>

29:16.296 --> 29:18.674
<i>You know,
I'm going to worry about myself.</i>

29:19.341 --> 29:20.217
<i>That's all.</i>

29:24.137 --> 29:25.097
Dre!

29:26.348 --> 29:28.100
The least you could do is give me a hug.

29:29.101 --> 29:31.019
The least you could do is give me a hug.

29:33.313 --> 29:34.147
So what?

29:36.108 --> 29:36.942
Hiya.

29:38.193 --> 29:40.153
- You all right?
