31:37.145 --> 31:38.563
Meth is no joke, but...

31:39.106 --> 31:41.066
the thought of wanting it so bad...

31:41.149 --> 31:42.692
it's just... I can taste it.

31:43.318 --> 31:46.405
It's not just in my home or my family,
it's everywhere.

31:48.448 --> 31:50.075
I'm ready to have my kids back.

31:51.410 --> 31:53.370
Determined to get them back in my life.

32:02.879 --> 32:04.005
Listen up.

32:04.089 --> 32:06.758
Do not touch anything on my cart,
do not talk to my unit workers.

32:06.842 --> 32:08.510
Grab your food and come back in this room.

32:10.929 --> 32:12.055
