34:06.336 --> 34:08.004
<i>see if we can get you out of there.</i>

34:11.424 --> 34:13.092
You talked to, um, Slim?

34:13.217 --> 34:14.928
<i>Yeah, I talked to him.</i>

34:15.344 --> 34:17.264
