35:14.279 --> 35:15.488
than it is in here.

35:18.908 --> 35:19.868
Mr. Russom?

35:20.535 --> 35:21.494
You're being released.

35:23.121 --> 35:25.498
<i>It was hard, to make your way
out of a situation</i>

35:25.582 --> 35:29.669
<i>where you're automatically seen as,
